You can simply ask Alexa to control your “Baby Monitor or other connected products”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:

(1). Download our “Maxi-Cosi Connected Home” app in app market then register an account;

(2). Configure our devices in our “Maxi-Cosi Connected Home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;

(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;

(4). Search “Maxi-Cosi Connected Home” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;

(5). Enable “Maxi-Cosi Connected Home” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Maxi-Cosi Connected Home” login page;

(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;

(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

“Alexa, turn on the Breathe humidifier.”
“Alexa, show me SEE baby monitor.”
“Alexa, brighten the Soothe light & sound to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom Glow Smart Light to 40%.”
"Alexa, set Breathe humidifier`s humidity to 55%."
"Alexa, turn on the Soothe light & sound lullaby music."
